        <section aria-label="Outside" class="card Card--card--2AzRg Card--cardPadded--2M25D Card--containerQuery--T7772" ctatext="See More" ctaurl="/slideshows" data-tb-region="db-cm-photos_EN" data-testid="ContentMediaModule" title="Outside">

         </header>

            <div class="mediaListItem ContentMedia--mediaListItem--bKPDd" data-tb-region-item="true">
